model.employees.drivers

Class SupplyDriver

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.employees.Employee
      • model.employees.drivers.Driver
        • model.employees.drivers.SupplyDriver
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class SupplyDriver
extends Driver
    Supply driver resupplies the warehouse with products that run out. The supply driver must traverse a distance of 4 to resupply a product, and his vehicle is a truck.
